{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>From the creators of the free experience Propagation VR, comes the first chapter of a thrilling new story.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trapped inside the Paradise Hotel, where a strange illness has turned people into savage creatures, you are desperate to find your sister. Play as Emily Diaz, explore dark surroundings, gather resources, and survive terrifying encounters. This intense single-player VR survival horror game with great storytelling will get your adrenaline pumping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">IMMERSIVE STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Emily's journey will take you through extreme emotions and intense phases of stealth, exploration or action. Meet allies and learn how to survive your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/41.gif?t=1737561647\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HORROR ATMOSPHERE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter the incredibly terrifying atmosphere of Propagation. The sound design, lighting, and visuals all combine to create a truly immersive experience that will keep you on edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/31.gif?t=1737561647\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAME MECHANICS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will need all your skills and your wits to progress:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Gather resources</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Solve puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Use tools from your inventory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Choose to avoid or confront enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Reload your gun under stress</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Free movement and teleportation locomotion support.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/21.gif?t=1737561647\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stay in touch with the game development! Follow and Wishlist on Steam, and check out <i>WanadevStudio</i> and <i>PropagationVR</i> on social media.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Goodbye My Friend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/03e3185a07cd7651bdc4d04f37343eea08509733.jpg"},{"name":"Hide-and-Seek","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/8e5340c94baf28078a97906bd265416afa5cde72.jpg"},{"name":"Right On Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/8c47f57c1ede622ae462dbd35f89d7e51f3b3553.jpg"},{"name":"Bring Out The Big Guns","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/cd0d4ffe5107727b7baa18955a4f780fc3f4f341.jpg"},{"name":"Sweet Revenge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/15d59bfe4821873518a8492d5b5209229bba055a.jpg"},{"name":"To Be Continued","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/862391ff5195759de2ae85557fb1db4d896fa034.jpg"},{"name":"Nightmare Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/e428b3c8aac697cf7e9adc6c436f2a8796472a63.jpg"},{"name":"Lightning Speed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/25353ee84696af4368673b4086afe5f21e9fc308.jpg"},{"name":"The Final Countdown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/5cc963531ef3194fdbe0844fe68e076c95560726.jpg"},{"name":"One Foot In The Grave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824960/b